<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="K_5743" type="Brief"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Andrea Podestà an Alfred Escher, Genua, Dienstag, 02. August 1870</title></titleStmt><publicationStmt><p>Digitale Briefedition Alfred Escher, Zürich: Alfred Escher-Stiftung.</p></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><msDesc><msIdentifier><institution>SBB Historic</institution><idno>VGB_GB_SBBGB01_006</idno></msIdentifier></msDesc><bibl type="printed"/></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><textClass><keywords scheme="http://briefedition.alfred-escher.ch/keywords"><term>Gotthardbahnprojekt</term><term>Italienisches Parlament</term></keywords></textClass><correspDesc><correspAction type="sent"><persName key="Podestà Andrea" type="addressee">Andrea Podestà</persName><persName key="Escher (vom Glas) Alfred" type="sender">Alfred Escher</persName><placeName>Genua</placeName><date when="1870-08-02">02. August 1870</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><placeName>Zürich</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="previous" target="B5389"/><ref type="next" target="B2496"/><ref type="previous-in-corresp" target="B5734"/></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><front>
      
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_5743_p1"><lb xml:id="p1-l1"/>
          <hi rend="printed">CABINETTO DEL SINDACO</hi>
        </p>
      
      <div type="dateline">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_5743_p2"><lb xml:id="p1-l2"/>
          <placeName key="Genua (I)">Genova</placeName>
          <date when="1870-08-02">2 Agosto 1870</date>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_5743_p3"><lb xml:id="p1-l3"/><choice><abbr>Preg<add>issi</add>mo</abbr><expan>Pregiatissimo</expan></choice> Signore</p>
      </div>
    </front><body>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_5743_p4"><lb xml:id="p1-l4"/>Non è punto minore in me
        <lb xml:id="p1-l5"/>
di quanto sia in Lei l`impegno
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l6"/>per una sollecita definizione della
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l7"/>pratica del <placeName key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">S. Gottardo</placeName>.</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_5743_p5"><lb xml:id="p1-l8"/>
Ma il nostro Parlamento si
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>trovò ora tanto stanco dalla lun<lb xml:id="p1-l10" break="no"/>ghissima sessione, che non fu pos<lb xml:id="p1-l11" break="no"/>sibile di portare a discussione la
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>relativa proposta di Legge.</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_5743_p6"><lb xml:id="p1-l13"/>
Spero però che alla prossima
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l14"/>riapertura della Camera dei
        
<pb n="2"/><lb xml:id="p2-l1"/>Deputati la cosa potrà essere
        
<lb xml:id="p2-l2"/>discussa.</p>
    </body><back>
      <div type="closer">
        <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_5743_p7"><lb xml:id="p2-l3"/>
Accolga i sentimenti della
        <lb xml:id="p2-l4"/>
più distinta mia considerazione.</p>
      </div>
      <div type="signature"><p rend="center" xml:id="K_5743_p8"><lb xml:id="p2-l5"/>Il Sindaco di <placeName key="Genua (I)">Genova</placeName> 
        <lb xml:id="p2-l6"/>A Podestà</p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_5743_p9"><lb xml:id="p2-l7"/>Preg<add>issi</add>mo<note type="transcript">Pregmo ist Abkürzung für Preg.mo = Pregiatissimo = Verehrtester</note> Signore
        
<lb xml:id="p2-l8"/>A. Escher
        
<lb xml:id="p2-l9"/><placeName key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zurigo</placeName> </p>
      </div>
    </back></text></TEI>